    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/b4cbaafcb6343f558a7206bf762a2f7d.webp?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/416c46d72a74009aa000858dd271b6b5.poster.avif?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/416c46d72a74009aa000858dd271b6b5.webm?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/416c46d72a74009aa000858dd271b6b5.mp4?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightness is measured from 8 points in your character, indicated by the outline. Stay hidden from guards to choke them from behind. After a successful knockout, don't forget to hide the body from patrolling guards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/8da2738c9b27e9f96dbd373c9c246e1e.webp?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/73dad6fb6204144f5391463593d31814.poster.avif?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/73dad6fb6204144f5391463593d31814.webm?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/73dad6fb6204144f5391463593d31814.mp4?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a mutant seagull armed with opposable thumbs, you can conquer the heights by climbing. Sail ships have climbable rigging, and the pipes in mines provide alternative routes. You can also slide down ropes and select the next climbable element in junction points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/f5ba143e580a41fac068d84bf505b471.webp?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/7737ade2691b4b021ec48e22a5cb2e4b.poster.avif?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/7737ade2691b4b021ec48e22a5cb2e4b.webm?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/7737ade2691b4b021ec48e22a5cb2e4b.mp4?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tools like grappling hooks, bombs, doze grenades, winches to lift gratings, and of course good old hand tools for some bludgeoning, can be found to clear your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/c81fc17ec54c8545476a8a03810c31e5.webp?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/f7d46e48fedf88dd67c6150c4d65a09d.poster.avif?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/f7d46e48fedf88dd67c6150c4d65a09d.webm?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/f7d46e48fedf88dd67c6150c4d65a09d.mp4?t=1760337002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objectives take you to sail ships, mines and rusted industrial buildings. Pick up a torch or lantern (which can be lit at stoves and burning barrels), to see where you're going. Just watch out for guards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/8cfee1ee3c333f6bd2ad973d89fc25c5.webp?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/b247079e68baa890c65daec0e1d1adb9.avif?t=1760337002\" width=600 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re the stealth expert in a crew sent on a mission across the seas to help defend their home town against an opposing force. There are currently 3 missions + tutorial (3-4 hours of content at minimum), with 2 more missions to come.</p>",
